    "Reason : 3 - INFORMATIVE\r\nNote to Applicant\r\nAccurate drawings including Existing and Proposed Side Elevations and details of materials for the proposal are required to be submitted with any future resubmisison.\r\n\r\nYou are informed that any calculation of the roofspace must also include the roof space created by the two storey side extension."
